George Coe https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Coe 0 George Coe (May 10, 1929 – July 18, 2015) was an American stage, film and television actor and voice artist. He did voice-over work in video games, movies and TV shows. He was a cast member for the first season of Saturday Night Live and voiced the character of Woodhouse in Archer.
